Job Responsibilities:

  Perform all monthly close activities
  Analyse performance of the business against budget/forecast and previous periods
  Reconciliation of accounts
  Perform cash flow forecast
  Participate in standard cost implementation
  Participate in annual budget and periodic forecast
  Assist in process improvements
  Involve in Accounts Receivable collection
  Prepare GST returns and EDB claims
  Handle the daily transaction processing which includes, purchase invoice processing and payments
  Issuing of Sales invoices and receipts recognition into the accounting system


Requirements:&nbsp;

  Degree in Accounting/Business Administration
  Knowledge of Microsoft Office
  ERP system
